A server-side application built on Spring and provides an REST endpoint. The application accepts requests with an English word as a parameter and return an output composed of 2 integers:
- The number of requests sent to this server with this word as a parameter
- The number of occurrences of this word in the attached set of text files (which comes from Project Gutenberg)

To run this project do:
- mvn clean install
- java -jar target/slicetest-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar
- curl 'http://localhost:8080/service?word=<qord to query>'
